story.text:
I'm a Software Engineer, Computer Scientist, and Mathematician. My home page
can be found at [http://www.cse.msu.edu/~dunham/ www.cse.msu.edu]

I'm currently working for a company in San Francisco called Clever Machine. I'm intrigued by XP, but haven't yet had a chance to use it. My
general computer science interests are learning new languages and techniques, and advancing the art of programming.
I also do a little work for the Debian Linux project.
If you're in the Bay area and want to get together for a beer, drop me an email.
